{"tid":1860262,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳偉霆廣州巡唱延期　粉絲：能不能不退票？","createTime":"2020-02-03T14:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T15:05:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"343789aa7ad86850958480e10efd4110a35b8720","tid":1860262,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:22:15.000Z","msg":"在內地爆紅的藝人陳偉霆原定於3月14日在廣州舉行巡迴演唱會，可是內地武漢肺炎疫情持續，今日其經理人霍汶希（Mani）在微博公布演唱會延期，她貼出公告指因近期的新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情，為響應當局及相關單位對疫情的管理及要求，及保障觀眾的健康與安全，陳偉霆的《一鼓作氣》巡迴演唱會廣州站延期舉行，但延開日期未定。<br />\n<br />\n至於退票安排，大會指可按照票面價值全額退款，不少陳偉霆粉絲紛紛留言表示不想退票，留言︰「延期不退票不行嗎？」「能不能不退票只延期，演唱會的票真的超級難搶啊！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200203/bkn-20200203143550142-0203_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200203%2Fbkn-20200203143550142-0203_00862_001.html&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdA5Iyec62GFiithg4eFnous%3D&h=93bed754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200203/bkn-20200203143550142-0203_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"af76a44df33402fc6b8d03df2eb61bf811354251","tid":1860262,"uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OdOxOEc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOdOxOEc.gif&h=46cde055&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec22bb3a84035123cfdca09e931a61d99882de69","tid":1860262,"uid":61745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:24:25.000Z","msg":"一鼓作氣，再而衰，三而歇。"},{"pid":"e8c55917a53db881a6a51f805a8b653d7fbd99d4","tid":1860262,"uid":158145,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:24:28.000Z","msg":"我可以代唱<br />\n<br />\n我啲friend話我唱歌似陳偉......屌，唔撚記得最尾個字係乜"},{"pid":"113d8b11da4feca29765b036cb2358ac0f4d6e55","tid":1860262,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T14:24:55.000Z","msg":"唔退，點食黃牛"},{"pid":"5